title: Keep me afloat in Tbilisi... AND get MYSTERY CONTENT!!
description:
Greetings from Tbilisi, Georgia. I am starting a subscription service to provide content that won't exactly fit with YouTube's format . Most of the reason for this has to do with copyright issues, Sometimes sound quality. And there are other reasons. I have many lectures and other content on a variety of subjects, from music history to reflections on the meaning of images, music and time. 

Your support will keep this channel healthy.The cost is quite modest. And can be handled either as a single contribution or as a monthly gift. 

Use PayPal. Or if you need to use another service let me know in the comment section below. Just CLICK here it's easy.
https://www.paypal.com/cgi-bin/webscr?cmd=_s-xclick&hosted_button_id=G9LDYMSPZ5RGG

Or send a message at The Anadromous Life Facebook page. 
https://www.facebook.com/theanadromist/

If you like what I'm doing here really consider helping me out. 
I appreciate your interest.
Byrne
